THE WRITING — CC0 1.0 Universal (public-domain dedication)
================================================================================

Covers all files under `src/content/`, and any data derived from them (the
downloadable archives, generated payloads, and the like). A change of format
does not change the dedication.

The author, Sergey Orekhov (Сергей Орехов, pen name Pancratius), dedicates these
writings to the public domain. No permission is required to read, copy,
translate, republish, train AI models on, fine-tune, summarize, perform, or
build upon them. Attribution is appreciated but not required.

